00:26.193 --> 00:28.326
¶ The weather started
getting rough ¶

00:28.395 --> 00:30.529
¶ the tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:30.597 --> 00:33.165
¶ if not for the courage
of the fearless crew ¶

00:33.234 --> 00:35.167
¶ the minnow would be lost ¶

00:35.236 --> 00:37.469
¶ the minnow would be lost ¶

00:37.538 --> 00:39.771
¶ the ship set ground
on the shore ¶

00:39.840 --> 00:42.641
¶ of this uncharted
desert isle ¶

00:42.710 --> 00:44.876
¶ with gilligan ¶

00:44.945 --> 00:47.312
¶ the skipper too ¶

00:47.381 --> 00:51.416
¶ the millionaire and his wife ¶

00:51.485 --> 00:54.586
¶ the movie star ¶

